</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_153" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_153_r1l1">VVolfram vom Eglofſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_153_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> wolfram . als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der ſprüch vnd ʒwytracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l4"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Jr gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l5">habt etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu ſein vns ſölıch ſache niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l6">kündıg vnd gönden eẅch wol daʒ Jr in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l7">wol weͣrt / <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> ſehen wır nıht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daʒ des Reıchs ſtraſſe ʒu vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l8">von vns beſchedıgt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nidergelegt . <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_line_1577035463642_3315"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Jacobȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_153" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wolfram vom Eglofstein</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wolfram, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der sprüch und
                        zwytracht <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir gen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        habt etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu sein uns sölich sache niht
                        kündig und gönden ewch wol, daz ir in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> wol weͣrt, <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sehen wir niht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz des reichs strasse zu und
                        von uns beschedigt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nidergelegt
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
